HEADWORD: Fairing
<hw>Fair"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>A present; originally, one given
or purchased at a fair.</def> <rj><au>Gay.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Fairing box</b></col>, <cd>a box receiving savings or
small sums of money.</cd> <rj><au>Hannah More.</au></rj></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

